      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "# v0.4.0 Release\r\n\r\n## 中文\r\n\r\n### feat\r\n\r\n* 支持通过插件设置生成自定义日记标题分区\r\n* 切换预览模式前自动保存当前笔记\r\n* 优化预览模式逻辑，仅在有有效内容时进入预览\r\n* 文件创建时，立刻更新界面相关元素\r\n\r\n### fix\r\n\r\n* 补充日记提示文本、笔记内容、输入框和预览区的深色模式样式\r\n* 修复 Obsidian 审核报错\r\n\r\n### refactor\r\n\r\n* 最低兼容 Obsidian 版本更新至 v1.7.2\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## English\r\n\r\n### feat\r\n\r\n* Support custom diary title sections via plugin settings\r\n* Auto-save current note before switching preview mode\r\n* Optimize preview logic to enter preview only when valid content exists\r\n* Update the relevant interface elements immediately when the file is created\r\n\r\n### fix\r\n\r\n* Add dark mode styles for diary hints, note content, input fields, and preview area\r\n* Fix Obsidian review validation error\r\n\r\n### refactor\r\n\r\n* Update minimum supported Obsidian version to v1.7.2\r\n\r\n",
