      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "0.3.0\r\n\r\nfeat(i18n): add full English/Chinese localization system with 60+ keys\r\nfeat(i18n): add language setting with auto-detect Obsidian locale on first launch\r\nfeat(i18n): internationalize all UI strings (calendar, weather, mood, settings, etc.)\r\nfeat(i18n): use locale-aware date and time formatting\r\n\r\nfeat(calendar): add start-of-week setting (Monday default / Sunday optional)\r\nfeat(calendar): extend calendar to full week layout (Mon–Sun / Sun–Sat)\r\nfeat(calendar): make weekday headers and grid respect start-of-week setting\r\nfeat(calendar): add configurable weekend highlight days\r\n\r\nfeat(settings): remove weather language and mood language settings, unify under global language\r\nrefactor(settings): reduce multiple language dropdowns into a single control\r\n\r\nfix(mobile): fix footer being obscured by Obsidian v1.12.7 tab bar\r\n\r\nchore(deps): update tsconfig lib target from ES6 to ES2020\r\n\r\n#1 ",
